    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/9feb8e96273842e405c6e6a1945971fe.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，艾露玛为了研究魔法用光了资金，无可奈何只好去酒馆接一些简单的委托，结果酒馆的前台给她推荐了某个委托。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然是个没有写明细节的奇怪委托，但由于报酬实在过于有吸引力，艾露玛无奈只好去找委托人询问情况……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/aa5e2857a41a8edcf8a6da9388b1dc6f.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.poster.avif?t=1759193652\" width=400 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.webm?t=1759193652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.mp4?t=1759193652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典的回合制RPG。艾露玛擅长使用魔法，所以用魔法作为主要手段打倒敌人吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关一个结局后，可以继承等级、金钱、学会的魔法开始新一轮游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中，TP累积到100时可以使用「魔法爆裂（简称M爆裂）」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用后，艾露玛的魔法攻击、回避、命中属性会得到强化，并解锁只有爆裂生效时才能使用的特殊魔法，但所有魔法需要消耗1.5倍的MP。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请在最佳的时机发动强大的M爆裂，挑战强敌吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/44214b29537af23f02a12304e6c6550a.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/fd5cacd907f7243efc7727906a21dc11.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/8d21d26ef440966e5305348670814ac4.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/141089d0ee81ee71725e4603e78308a4.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p>",
